Key changes:
- `<div className="space-y-2">` becomes `<Field orientation="vertical">`
- `<Label>` becomes `<FieldLabel>` (preserves `htmlFor` and required asterisk styling)
- `<p className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">` becomes `<FieldDescription>` (adds `aria-describedby`)
- `<p className="text-xs text-red-500">` becomes `<FieldError errors={...} />` (adds `role="alert"`)
- `helpMarkdown` Collapsible section is unchanged

